  "description": "A small QOL mod that lets you alter the vanilla crosshair in small ways.",
  "body": "<a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/microcontrollers\" target=\"_blank\">\n  <img alt=\"kofi-singular-alt\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/donate/kofi-singular-alt_vector.svg\">\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://codeberg.org/MicrocontrollersDev/CrosshairTweaks\" target=\"_blank\">\n  <img alt=\"codeberg\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/available/codeberg_vector.svg\">\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/crosshair-tweaks\" target=\"_blank\">\n  <img alt=\"curseforge\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/available/curseforge_vector.svg\">\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/connector\" target=\"_blank\">\n  <img alt=\"sinytra connector\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/6j289t.svg\">\n</a>\n\n# Crosshair Tweaks\n\nA small QOL mod that lets you alter the vanilla crosshair in small ways.\n\n## Features\n\n### Normal Crosshair\n\n- Disable Crosshair\n- Hide in Containers\n- Show in Third Person\n- Always Show in Spectator\n- Remove Crosshair Blending\n- Remove Attack Indicator Blending\n- Crosshair Opacity\n- Attack Indicator Opacity\n\n### Debug Crosshair\n\n- Ignore Debug Crosshair\n- Always Use Debug Crosshair\n\n## Recommended\n\nI also recommend using [Centered Crosshair](https://modrinth.com/mod/centered-crosshair)!",
